{"title":"The New Thousand Heritage 2.0 Helmet is More Ventilated, Visible, & Fits More Diverse Riders","link":"https://bikerumor.com/thousand-heritage-2-0-helmet-review/","date":1680803119000,"content":"<p>There are a lot of race-focused helmets out there, but the helmets from Thousand take a much different approach. Designed to be stylish yet functional, the original Thousand Heritage helmet stood out from a sea of aggressively styled helmets. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Like any product though, improvements can be made. One of the biggest improvements that Thousand wanted to make to the helmet was making it fit more riders in an effort to be more inclusive to all. That meant introducing what they’re calling a “unique hybrid head form that is designed with both the Asian (round) and European (oval) head shapes.” Thousand points out that most helmet companies fit the latter headform, so the new Thousand headform should comfortably fit more riders globally. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>In terms of sizing, the Heritage 2.0 is offered in three sizes, Small (54-57cm), Medium (57-59cm), and Large (59-62cm). The fit is certainly different from a lot of helmets that I’ve tried – at 56cm, I’m typically on the small side of a medium. The size guide for Thousand puts me in a small, which <em>just</em> fits but it’s a little tight at the temples. However, my wife whose head measures 55cm (and is more oval shaped) fits perfectly in the small. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-05.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-05-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"inside of Thousand Heritage 2.0 helmet\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-05-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-05-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-05-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-05-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-05-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-05-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-05.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-04.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-04-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Thousand Heritage 2.0 helmet cradle\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-04-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-04-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-04-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-04-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-04-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-04-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-04.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-03.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-03-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Thousand Heritage 2.0 helmet straps\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-03-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-03-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-03-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-03-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-03-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-03-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-03.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>I would say that the sizing is generally a bit bigger than other helmets out there, though I think I would still prefer the medium for my head. Adjustments are made with the dial fit system and internal cradle that offers three vertical positions. The vegan leather straps don’t have any ear cradle adjustment, but they’re well-positioned and fasten with a magnetic Fidlock buckle. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-07.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-07-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Thousand Heritage 2.0 helmet top vents\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-07-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-07-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-07-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-07-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-07-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-07-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-07.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-06.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-06-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Thousand Heritage 2.0 helmet brow vents\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-06-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-06-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-06-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-06-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-06-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-06-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-06.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Improved Ventilation</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Outside of the change in fit profile, the outer shell has been updated as well. Increased ventilation at the top of the helmet should make it a bit more comfortable in hot weather. While the front of the helmet lacks any visible venting, the inner brow of the helmet has internally molded channels that allow air to flow from the front of the helmet, and out the top and back. All together, Thousand claims this is responsible for a whopping 70% increase in ventilation from the original Heritgage helmet.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-09.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-09-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Thousand Heritage 2.0 helmet poplock out\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-09-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-09-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-09-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-09-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-09-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-09-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-09.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-08.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-08-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Thousand Heritage 2.0 helmet poplock\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-08-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-08-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-08-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-08-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-08-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-08-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-08.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>PopLock Still Popping</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Unlike many of the helmets on the market, the Heritage 2.0 is not an in-molded design meaning there is a hard plastic outer shell with an inner EPS layer. That makes it more durable for daily use including locking it up to the bike – which is a perfect time to use their patented PopLock. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The magnetic PopLock cover is tethered to the helmet, so you can easily pop it out, thread your lock through it, and lock it to the bike. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/thousand-features-helmet-h2-tail-light-carbon-black.jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"720\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/thousand-features-helmet-h2-tail-light-carbon-black.jpg.webp\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/thousand-features-helmet-h2-tail-light-carbon-black.jpg.webp 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/thousand-features-helmet-h2-tail-light-carbon-black.jpg-297x206.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/thousand-features-helmet-h2-tail-light-carbon-black.jpg-120x83.webp 120w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-10.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-10-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Thousand Heritage 2.0 helmet magnetic light mount\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-10-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-10-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-10-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-10-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-10-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-10-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-10.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Increased Visibility</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The Heritage 2.0 gets another magnetic party trick as well with the addition of a new magnetic tail light. When available this summer, the light will be sold separately for $25 and will simply pop onto the back of the helmet. Then you can easily remove it when locking up the helmet or to recharge it. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-02.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-02-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Thousand Heritage 2.0 helmet actual weight\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-02-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-02-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-02-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-02-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-02-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-02-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-02.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Thousand Heritage 2.0 Helmet Actual Weight</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A non-in-molded helmet will typically be heavier, and that’s the case with the Heritage 2.0. At 455g, the helmet is on the heavier side, but it’s both CPSC certified for bikes <em>and </em>ASTM F1492-15 certified for skateboarding and roller skating. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2-helmet-colors.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"419\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2-helmet-colors-800x419.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2-helmet-colors-800x419.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2-helmet-colors-297x156.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2-helmet-colors-120x63.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2-helmet-colors-768x402.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2-helmet-colors-1536x805.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2-helmet-colors.jpg 1670w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-01.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-01-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Thousand Heritage 2.0 helmet bag\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-01-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-01-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-01-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-01-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-01-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Thousand-Heritage-2.0-bike-helmet-01.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Pricing, Colors, &amp; Availability</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Offered in eight standard colors with additional seasonal colors coming soon, the Heritage 2.0 is available now for $99 with the option to add a monogram for $17-19. You also get their free accident replacement program where if you have an accident and your helmet is damaged, they’ll replace it for free. Also, each helmet ships in an environmentally friendly bamboo fiber bag, and Thousand has been a Climate Positive business since 2020 by offsetting 110% of their carbon emissions. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.explorethousand.com/products/bike-helmet-2\" target=\"_blank\">explorethousand.com</a></em></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/thousand-heritage-2-0-helmet-review/\">The New Thousand Heritage 2.0 Helmet is More Ventilated, Visible, &amp; Fits More Diverse Riders</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Zach Overholt","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"fb0b68731dc422dceabbd2475f531e71cd0a65f713771af9f30301ea34b1a00e","category":"Cycling"}